<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>签到</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/bootstrap.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/bootstrap-theme.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/register.css">
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container-fluid header">
    <h4 class="title">签到</h4>
    <p class="text">
      学员请填写签到信息，如已报名，需要和报名的信息保持一致，点击“签到”按钮。
    </p>
    <div class="line"></div>
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <div class="row">
        <form action="" method="post" class="col-md-push-2 col-md-10 form">
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 left">
                <label for="name">姓名 <span>*</span></label>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
                <input name="name" id="name" class="col-md-4 form-control" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 left">
                <label for="gender">性别 <span>*</span></label>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
                <select class="form-control" id="gender" name="gender">
                  <option>男</option>
                  <option>女</option>
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 left">
                <label for="phone">手机号码 <span>*</span></label>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
                <input name="phone" id="phone" class="col-md-4 form-control" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 left">
                <label for="danWeiName">单位名称</label>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
                <input name="danWeiName" id="danWeiName" class="col-md-4 form-control" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 left">
                <label for="zhuSu">报名班级 <span>*</span></label>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
                <select class="form-control" id="zhuSu" name="zhuSu">
                  <option>是</option>
                  <option>否</option>
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 left">
                <label for="invoice">是否已缴费 <span>*</span></label>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
                <select class="form-control" id="invoice" name="invoice">
                  <option>是</option>
                  <option>否</option>
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 left">
                <label for="danWeiName">转账凭证/订单号</label>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
                <input name="danWeiName" id="danWeiName" class="col-md-4 form-control" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-push-1 col-md-8 col-sm-6 submit">
                <button type="submit" name="submit" class="btn btn-primary">签到</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>  
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

